snippet: The final stretch of the United States Senate campaign in New Jersey was jolted Thursday by the death of the father of the Democratic candidate, Mayor Cory A. Booker of Newark.
abstract: Final stretch of United States Senate campaign in New Jersey, already more unpredictable than expected, is jolted again by death of father of Democratic candidate Mayor Cory A Booker of Newark; Cary Booker, 76, died in Las Vegas after long illness.
lead_paragraph: The final stretch of the United States Senate campaign in New Jersey was jolted Thursday by the death of the father of the Democratic candidate, Mayor Cory A. Booker of Newark.

headline.main: Booker’s Father Dies After Long Illness
headline.print_headline: Booker’s Father Dies After Long Illness
